sourceId = g3a_u01_3a01
status = WAITING_FOR_LOCAL_TEST

root_cause:
- G3A-U01 source-unit mode now includes the existing comparison PatternSpec plus the new number-structure PatternSpecs.
- The previous route only handled plans where every PatternSpec was a number-structure spec.
- Source-unit smoke therefore fell through to the base expression generator, which attempted to read expression ranges from number-structure definitions.

fixed:
- widened the G3A-U01 route to support comparison plus number-structure specs.
- added a local comparison generator for ps_g3a_u01_4digit_compare inside the G3A-U01 route.
- added source-unit regression coverage for mixed comparison and number-structure worksheet generation.

local_check:
- git pull public main
- npm test
- git status

next = S44M_G3A_U01_MixedWorksheetQA after local tests pass
